## 6B: File Consolidation

### Filesystem tools â†’ fs.ex

Three single-module files with no shared private functions:

| Before | Lines |
|--------|-------|
| `fs_read.ex` | 57 |
| `fs_write.ex` | 40 |
| `fs_edit.ex` | 64 |
| **Total** | **161** |

**After:** One file `apps/rho_stdlib/lib/rho/stdlib/tools/fs.ex` (161 lines)
containing all three modules. Module names unchanged â€” `Rho.Stdlib.Tools.FsRead`,
`FsWrite`, `FsEdit` â€” so no callers needed updating.

### Tape tools â†’ tape_tools.ex

Four tool modules that all follow the same pattern (closure over `tape_name`):

| Before | Lines |
|--------|-------|
| `anchor.ex` | 50 |
| `search_history.ex` | 49 |
| `recall_context.ex` | 98 |
| `clear_memory.ex` | 43 |
| **Total** | **240** |

**After:** One file `apps/rho_stdlib/lib/rho/stdlib/tools/tape_tools.ex` (240 lines)
containing all four modules. Module names unchanged.

### AgentLoop internals â†’ Runner + Recorder

Runner.ex was 639 lines before this change (>350 threshold), so Recorder
stays as a separate module but is flattened out of the `AgentLoop` namespace.

| Before | After |
|--------|-------|
| `Rho.AgentLoop.Runtime` (67 lines, in `agent_loop/runtime.ex`) | `Rho.Runner.Runtime` (inlined in `runner.ex`) |
| `Rho.AgentLoop.Tape` (26 lines, in `agent_loop/tape.ex`) | `Rho.Runner.TapeConfig` (inlined in `runner.ex`) |
| `Rho.AgentLoop.Recorder` (174 lines, in `agent_loop/recorder.ex`) | `Rho.Recorder` (in `recorder.ex`) |

The `agent_loop/` directory is now deleted entirely. References updated in:

- `apps/rho/lib/rho/runner.ex` â€” aliases
- `apps/rho/lib/rho/recorder.ex` â€” new file, new module name
- `apps/rho/test/support/turn_strategy_harness.ex` â€” aliases + struct refs
- `apps/rho/test/rho/turn_strategy/typed_structured_test.exs` â€” struct refs

### Line count summary

| Area | Before (files) | After (files) | Lines saved |
|------|---------------|--------------|-------------|
| Tape.Context shims | 2 | 0 | -31 |
| active_mounts alias | 1 function | 0 | -1 |
| fs tools | 3 files | 1 file | 0 (same content) |
| tape tools | 4 files | 1 file | 0 (same content) |
| AgentLoop directory | 3 files | 0 (inlined/flattened) | 0 (same content) |
| **Net file reduction** | **12 files** | **2 files** | **-10 files** |

